# 🧵 Sockets and Pipes 

This repository contains my notes, code examples, and exercises as I work through the book  
**_Sockets and Pipes_** by Chris Martin and Julie Moronuki — a deep dive into functional programming, input/output, and concurrency using **Haskell**.

